These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, thriller, martial-arts, time-travel
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, reggae, trance, ambient
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, british, russian, pakistani
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, motorbike, quad-bike, ship
1. the british is the fan of ambient##1
2. the russian is between the person watching martial-arts movies and the person watching time-travel movies##2
3. the british is the person driving the car##1
4. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person driving the car##1
5. the fan of house is on the left of the chinese##1
6. the person driving the quad-bike is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
7. the fan of reggae is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
8. the chinese is on the far right##1
9. the person watching thriller movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | time-travel   | superhero  | martial-arts  |
| Music-Genre   | reggae    | ambient    | house      | trance    |
| Nationality   | pakistani | british | russian | chinese |
| Transport     | ship  | car       | motorbike    | quad-bike     |

