.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, chess, collecting, baking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, documentary, disaster, mystery
4 different pets are kept: horse, mouse, rabbit, chinchilla
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, golf, sailing, parkour
1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is the person who's sport is golf##1
4. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
5. the person watching mystery movies is between the owner of the rabbit and the person who's sport is badminton##2
6. the person who's sport is parkour is between the person watching mystery movies and the owner of the chinchilla##2
7. the owner of the horse is on the far right##1
8. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
9. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | baking | chess    | collecting  | puzzles    |
| Movie-Genre   | spy      | documentary  | mystery  | disaster |
| Pet           | chinchilla      | rabbit       | mouse      | horse       |
| Sport         | golf    | parkour | sailing | badminton |

