.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
There 4 different types of food: papaya, pumpkin, apricot, corn
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, drawing, hiking, sudoku
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, chef, software-developer, mechanic
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, airplane, ship, train
1. the software-developer is the person driving the airplane##1
2. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the mechanic##1
3. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
4. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
5. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
6. the chef is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
7. the person eating corn is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
8. the person eating papaya is between the person who's hobby is gardening and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
9. the person who's hobby is hiking is between the person eating apricot and the chef##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Food        | pumpkin | apricot     | papaya   | corn     |
| Hobby       | drawing   | gardening   | hiking | sudoku |
| Job         | architect   | software-developer | mechanic       | chef    |
| Transport   | ship    | airplane | jet-ski  | train    |

