.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, engineer, nurse, journalist
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, western, epic, drama
4 different pets are kept: turtle, goldfish, dog, goat
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, rowing, snowboarding, lacrosse
 1. the person watching western movies is on the far right##1
 2. the person watching drama movies is the entrepreneur##1
 3. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching drama movies is the owner of the goldfish##1
 6. the owner of the goat is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 7. the person watching western movies is the nurse##1
 8. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
 9. the entrepreneur is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
10. the engineer is between the owner of the turtle and the journalist##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Job           | entrepreneur  | journalist | engineer     | nurse |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | crime  | epic | western       |
| Pet           | goldfish       | goat    | dog      | turtle           |
| Sport         | weightlifting | rowing   | lacrosse   | snowboarding         |

