 4. the videographer is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 5. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
 6. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
 7. the doctor is on the left of the person eating onion##1
 8. the mechanic is the person watching spy movies##1
 9. the person eating broccoli is between the person who's sport is skiing and the person watching time-travel movies##2
10. the person watching action movies is the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
