2. the chef is between the fan of d&b and the pakistani##2
3. the nigerian is between the person who's sport is badminton and the american##2
4. the coach is on the left of the american##1
5. the nigerian is the nigerian##1
6. the american is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
7. the american is on the left of the musician##1
8. the fan of rock is on the far right##1
9. the fan of metal is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Job           | coach | chef | musician  | project-manager |
| Music-Genre   | metal      | salsa       | d&b     | rock      |
| Nationality   | pakistani   | american      | nigerian   | spanish   |
| Sport         | soccer   | tennis    | basketball | badminton   |

