 5. the brazilian is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
 6. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 7. the egyptian is the person driving the tram##1
 8. the fan of hip-hop is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
10. the canadian is the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
