4. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
5. the person driving the train is between the person driving the tram and the person watching disaster movies##2
6. the person drinking fanta is the person watching scientific movies##1
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
8. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1

