The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, board-games, camping, drawing
4 different pets are kept: mouse, guinea-pig, hedgehog, fish
 1. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
 2. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 4. the person eating artichoke is the person drinking cola##1
 5. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking water##1
 6. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1
 7. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 8. the owner of the fish is between the person eating artichoke and the person eating watermelon##2
 9. the person eating papaya is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
10. the person who's hobby is dancing is between the person eating artichoke and the person eating watermelon##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| Beverage   | cola    | tea    | water      | 7up |
| Food       | artichoke        | papaya       | watermelon       | pepper     |
| Hobby      | camping | dancing | drawing | board-games        |
| Pet        | guinea-pig       | fish     | hedgehog         | mouse           |

